<script type="text/javascript">
    $(document).ready(function () {
        var Companylbl = $('#Companylbl').val();
        var BusinessUnitlbl = $('#BusinessUnitlbl').val();
        var CostCenterlbl = $('#CostCenterlbl').val();
        var IsCompanyVisible = $('#CompanylblIsMandatory').val();
        var IsBusinessUnitVisible = $('#BusinessUnitlblIsMandatory').val();
        var IsCostCenterVisible = $('#CostCenterlblIsMandatory').val();

        //#region Set default values of Company, Business Unit and Cost Center from ViewData to Variable
        var DCompanyId = 'null';
        var DBusinessUnitId = 'null';
        var DCostCenterId = 'null';
        //#endregion

        //#region Bind Company List on load of partial view
        if (IsCompanyVisible != undefined) { // Changes on 09092015 to set default value of Company from  Set Transaction default screen 
            getCompanyList();
            if (DCompanyId != "null" && DCompanyId != undefined) {
                $("#CompanyId").val(DCompanyId);
                $("#CompanyId").trigger("liszt:updated");
            }
        }
        //#endregion

        //#region Business Unit List on load of partial view if Company is not visble but Business Unit is Visible
        //if (IsCompanyVisible == undefined && IsBusinessUnitVisible != undefined) {
        if (IsBusinessUnitVisible != undefined) { // Changes on 09092015 to set default value of Business Unit from  Set Transaction default screen 
            getBusinessUnitList();
            if (DBusinessUnitId != "null" && DBusinessUnitId != undefined) {
                $("#BusinessUnitId").val(DBusinessUnitId);
                $("#BusinessUnitId").trigger("liszt:updated");
            }
        }
        //#endregion

        //#region Cost Center List  on load of partial view if Company and Business Unit are not visble but Cost Center is Visible
        //if ((IsCompanyVisible == undefined || IsBusinessUnitVisible == undefined) && IsCostCenterVisible != undefined) {
        if (IsCostCenterVisible != undefined) { // Changes on 09092015 to set default value of Cost Center from  Set Transaction default screen 
            getCostCeneterList();
            if (DCostCenterId != "null" && DCostCenterId != undefined) {
                $("#CostCenterId").val(DCostCenterId);
                $("#CostCenterId").trigger("liszt:updated");
            }
        }
        //#endregion 

        //#region on Company dropdown change to populate business units
        $('#CompanyId').change(function () {
            getBusinessUnitList();
        });
        //#endregion 

        //#region On Business Unit dropdown chnage populate cost center  
        $('#BusinessUnitId').change(function () {
            getCostCeneterList();            
        });
        //#endregion 

        //#region populate compnay list
        function getCompanyList() {
            $.gorillaAjax({
                type: "GET",
                contentType: "application/json; charset=utf-8",
                url: '/AjaxCall/GetCompanyList/',
                dataType: "json",
                async: false,
                cache: true,
                cacheType: "session",
                success: function (data) {
                    $("#CompanyId").empty();
                    var optionhtml1 = '<option value="' + 0 + '">' + "--Select--" + '</option>';
                    $("#CompanyId").append(optionhtml1);
                    $.each(data, function (i) {
                        var optionhtml = '<option value="' +
                    data[i].CompanyId + '">' + data[i].CompanyName + '</option>';
                        $("#CompanyId").append(optionhtml);
                    });                   
                }
            });
        }
        //#endregion 

        //#region populate business Unit List 
        function getBusinessUnitList() {
            if (IsBusinessUnitVisible != undefined) {
                var selectedCompanyId = $('#CompanyId').val();
                var URL = '/AjaxCall/GetBusinessUnitList/';
                if (selectedCompanyId != undefined) {
                    URL += '?CompanyId=' + selectedCompanyId;
                }
                $.gorillaAjax({
                    type: "GET",
                    contentType: "application/json; charset=utf-8",
                    url: URL,
                    dataType: "json",
                    async: false,
                    cache: true,
                    cacheType: "session",
                    success: function (data) {
                        $("#BusinessUnitId").empty();
                        $("#CostCenterId").empty();
                        $("#CostCenterId").append('<option value="' + 0 + '">' + "--Select--" + '</option>');
                        var optionhtml1 = '<option value="' + 0 + '">' + "--Select--" + '</option>';
                        $("#BusinessUnitId").append(optionhtml1);
                        $.each(data, function (i) {
                            var optionhtml = '<option value="' + data[i].BusinessUnitId + '">' + data[i].BusinessUnitDescription + '</option>';
                            $("#BusinessUnitId").append(optionhtml);
                        });                      
                    }
                });
            } else {
                getCostCeneterList(); //If Business Unit field is not enabed but the cost center is enabled
            }
        }
        //#endregion 

        //#region populate Cost center list
        function getCostCeneterList() {

            if (IsCostCenterVisible != undefined) {
                var CompanyId = $('#CompanyId').val();
                var BusinessUnitId = $('#BusinessUnitId').val();
                var URL = '/AjaxCall/GetCostCenterList/?';
                if (CompanyId != undefined) {
                    URL += 'CompanyId=' + CompanyId + "&";
                }
                if (BusinessUnitId != undefined) {
                    URL += 'BusinessUnitId=' + BusinessUnitId;
                }
                $.gorillaAjax({
                    type: "GET",
                    contentType: "application/json; charset=utf-8",
                    url: URL,
                    dataType: "json",
                    async: false,
                    cache: true,
                    cacheType: "session",
                    success: function (data) {
                        $("#CostCenterId").empty();
                        var optionhtml1 = '<option value="' + 0 + '">' + "--Select--" + '</option>';
                        $("#CostCenterId").append(optionhtml1);
                        $.each(data, function (i) {
                            var optionhtml = '<option value="' + data[i].CostCenterId + '">' + data[i].Description + '</option>';
                            $("#CostCenterId").append(optionhtml);
                        });                    
                    }
                });
            }
        }
        //#endregion
    });
</script>
